    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, peel and finely chop (or grate) the garlic</p>\r\n<p><strong>Cut</strong>&nbsp;1/2&nbsp;<span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span>&nbsp;chilli in half lengthways, scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon and chop finely</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> keep the seeds in if you dare!</p>\r\n<p><strong>Strip</strong> the thyme leaves from their stems and chop finely</p>",
